== 第2季 ==
这部剧集在2015年8月8日被续订第2季。<ref>{{Cite tweet |number=630030865054109698 |user=netflix |title=Birthdays are just the beginning. #sense8 is reborn. |date=2015-08-08 |author=网飞 |authorlink=网飞 |accessdate=2015-08-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160509122847/https://twitter.com/netflix/status/630030865054109698 |archivedate=2016-05-09 |deadurl=no |language=en, es, ko}}</ref>在2015年12月月底和次年1月月底的两次短暂摄制之后，主要的摄制过程于2016年开始。<ref name="thefilmstage">{{cite interview |url=http://thefilmstage.com/features/john-toll-talks-adjusting-for-the-small-screen-sense8-the-wachowskis-more/ |title=John Toll Talks Adjusting for the Small Screen, 'Sense8,' the Wachowskis & More |subject=John Toll |interviewer=Nick Newman |date=2015-11-24 |work=The Film Stage |accessdate=2015-11-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160509123101/https://thefilmstage.com/features/john-toll-talks-adjusting-for-the-small-screen-sense8-the-wachowskis-more/ |archivedate=2016-05-09 |deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref><ref name="winter2015shoot">{{Cite tweet |number=677686834613379073 |user=straczynski |title=@JanMSchroeder It's a separate shoot to grab footage during the holiday, not the start of full-on main unit shooting. |date=2015-12-17 |author=J. Michael Straczynski |authorlink=约瑟夫·迈克尔·斯特拉日恩斯基 |accessdate=2015-12-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160509132830/https://twitter.com/straczynski/status/677686834613379073 |archivedate=2016-05-09 |deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref><ref name="reelchicago">{{cite web |url=http://reelchicago.com/article/three-new-shows-set-cinespace-ready-roll160121 |title=Three new shows set up at Cinespace ready to roll |author=Ruth L Ratny |date=2016-01-21 |work=ReelChicago |accessdate=2016-01-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160509123904/http://reelchicago.com/article/three-new-shows-set-cinespace-ready-roll160121 |archivedate=2016-05-09 |deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref>第2季的摄制于9月16日殺青。<ref name="wrapS2MPC">{{Cite tweet |user=MPC_UK |author=Motion Picture Capital |number=777934880357421057 |title=Congratulations to cast & crew for wrapping up the incredible achievement / feat of endurance that is filming #Sense8Season2! |date=2016-09-19 |accessdate=2016-09-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160919232653/https://twitter.com/MPC_UK/status/777934880357421057 |archivedate=2016-09-19 |deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref><ref name="wrapS2Brian">{{Cite tweet |user=BrianJacobSmith |author=Brian J. Smith |authorlink=布萊恩·J·史密斯 |number=778147426154717184 |title=That's a wrap on @sense8 season 2. It was the adventure of a lifetime. |date=2016-09-20 |accessdate=2016-09-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160920082818/https://twitter.com/BrianJacobSmith/status/778147426154717184 |archivedate=2016-09-20 |deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite AV media |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VN_RJcV64ME |title=JMS Spotlight SDCC 2016 |date=2016-07-24 |author=Jan Schroeder |type=Recording |via=[[YouTube|YouTube]] |time=19:22 |accessdate=2016-12-03| language=en}} The video has been [https://twitter.com/straczynski/status/757454708751540225 retweeted] by [[约瑟夫·迈克尔·斯特拉日恩斯基|约瑟夫·迈克尔·斯特拉日恩斯基]].</ref> 2016年12月3日，Netflix宣布第2季将会于2017年5月5日发布。<ref name="s2dates"/>

2016年12月25日，第一集作为“圣诞特别集”宣传并发布，<ref name="s2dates">{{cite web |url=http://collider.com/sense8-season-2-release-date/ |title='Sense8' Returns to Netflix for Christmas Special; Season 2 Release Date Revealed |author=Dave Trumbore |date=2016-12-03 |accessdate=2016-12-04 |work=[[Collider.com|Collider.com]]|publisher={{tsl|en|Complex Media|}}|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161204213909/http://collider.com/sense8-season-2-release-date/ |archivedate=2016-12-04| deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vulture.com/2016/12/sense8-recap-season-1-episode-13.html |title=Sense8 Christmas Special Recap: 'Tis the Season |author=Simon Abrams |date=2016-12-23 |work={{tsl|en|Vulture.com|}}|publisher={{tsl|en|New York Media|}}|accessdate=2016-12-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170111000839/http://www.vulture.com/2016/12/sense8-recap-season-1-episode-13.html |archivedate=2017-01-11 |deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref>随后更名为“去他妈的新年快乐”，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://nique.net/entertainment/2017/01/13/sense8-loses-sense-of-plot/ |title=Sense8 loses sense of plot |author=Monica Jamison |date=2017-01-13 |work=Technique |accessdate=2017-01-13 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170113195449/http://nique.net/entertainment/2017/01/13/sense8-loses-sense-of-plot/ |archivedate=2017-01-13 |deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref>是一个时长2小时的{{tsl|en|Christmas by medium#Television specials and episodes||圣诞特别集}}。它于2016年12月3日在圣保罗{{tsl|en|Comic Con Experience|动漫体验展}}上放映。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://noticiasdatv.uol.com.br/noticia/series/orgia-com-protagonistas-de-sense8-leva-publico-da-comic-con-ao-delirio--13414 |title=Orgia com protagonistas de Sense8 leva público da Comic Con ao delírio |author=João da Paz |date=2016-12-04 |work=Notícias da TV |accessdate=2016-12-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161204213238/http://noticiasdatv.uol.com.br/noticia/series/orgia-com-protagonistas-de-sense8-leva-publico-da-comic-con-ao-delirio--13414 |archivedate=2016-12-04 |deadurl=no  |language=pt-br}}</ref>随后两集在2017年4月13日至23日在巴黎举行的剧集狂欢节期间放映。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/jim-carreys-im-dying-up-premiere-at-paris-fest-987926 |title=Jim Carrey's'I'm Dying Up Here' to Premiere at Paris Fest |author=Rhonda Richford  |date=2017-03-22 |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |publisher=[[Prometheus_Global_Media|Prometheus Global Media]] |accessdate=2017-03-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170323185451/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/jim-carreys-im-dying-up-premiere-at-paris-fest-987926 |archivedate=2017-03-23 |deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref>


